docs/combat_authority_map.md:91:Current finding: the CLI is a real consumer of shared combat surfaces, but full CLI smoke proof is outside S03. `docs/m015_failure_ledger.md` records remaining consumer-side work, including the runtime initialization and cwd-sensitive asset loading boundary owned by downstream slices.
